    Then I should not see a member link to "Embiggen"

    When I follow "View"
    Then I should not see an action item link to "Embiggen"

    When I follow "Edit Post"
    Then I should not see an action item link to "Embiggen"

    When I am on the index page for posts
    And I follow "New Post"
    Then I should not see an action item link to "Embiggen"
